<item>
            <title>[PDFBOX-3106] Allow access to font data</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-3106</link>
                <project id="12310760" key="PDFBOX">PDFBox</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In CFFFont we used to have:&lt;br/&gt;
public Map&amp;lt;String, byte[]&amp;gt; getCharStringsDict()&lt;br/&gt;
now we have:&lt;br/&gt;
List&amp;lt;byte[]&amp;gt; getCharStringBytes()&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Also we used to be able to create our own new MaximumProfileTable() but this is not public anymore.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Can it be public also.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
