                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="15004446" author="jahewson" created="Fri, 13 Nov 2015 18:25:37 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Why?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15006360" author="ssteiner1" created="Mon, 16 Nov 2015 08:58:25 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;We use it to merge fonts&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15018333" author="jahewson" created="Fri, 20 Nov 2015 17:01:24 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Ok, I&apos;ll make that CFFFont method public.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Also we used to be able to create our own new MaximumProfileTable() but this is not public anymore.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;You can&apos;t create any tables anymore, because FontBox can&apos;t write them. Basically FontBox is read-only, those setter methods were only for TTFParser in 1.8, which is why they&apos;re now private in 2.0. If you&apos;re wanting to manipulate a FontBox font then I&apos;d recommend doing it like TTFSubsetter does and then just parse the result as a new FontBox font. I assume as you&apos;re writing to the font file you must be doing something somewhat similar at the moment (as FontBox doesn&apos;t support writing).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15018349" author="jira-bot" created="Fri, 20 Nov 2015 17:12:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 1715394 from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=jahewson&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;jahewson&quot;&gt;jahewson&lt;/a&gt; in branch &apos;pdfbox/trunk&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://svn.apache.org/r1715394&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://svn.apache.org/r1715394&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-3106&quot; title=&quot;Allow access to font data&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-3106&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-3106&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Public access to charstring bytes&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15018350" author="jira-bot" created="Fri, 20 Nov 2015 17:13:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 1715395 from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=jahewson&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;jahewson&quot;&gt;jahewson&lt;/a&gt; in branch &apos;pdfbox/trunk&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://svn.apache.org/r1715395&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://svn.apache.org/r1715395&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-3106&quot; title=&quot;Allow access to font data&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-3106&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-3106&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Public access to charstring bytes (+ final)&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15018355" author="jira-bot" created="Fri, 20 Nov 2015 17:13:57 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 1715396 from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=jahewson&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;jahewson&quot;&gt;jahewson&lt;/a&gt; in branch &apos;pdfbox/trunk&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://svn.apache.org/r1715396&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://svn.apache.org/r1715396&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-3106&quot; title=&quot;Allow access to font data&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-3106&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-3106&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Public access to charstring bytes (+ unmodifiable)&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15018357" author="jahewson" created="Fri, 20 Nov 2015 17:14:17 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Ok, now in 2.0 you can get the charstring bytes by glyph name as follows:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;CFFType1Font font = ...
&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;byte&lt;/span&gt;[] bytes = font.getCharStringBytes(font.nameToGID(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;foo&quot;&lt;/span&gt;));
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15020442" author="jira-bot" created="Sat, 21 Nov 2015 12:53:09 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 1715509 from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=lehmi&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;lehmi&quot;&gt;lehmi&lt;/a&gt; in branch &apos;pdfbox/trunk&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://svn.apache.org/r1715509&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://svn.apache.org/r1715509&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-3106&quot; title=&quot;Allow access to font data&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-3106&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-3106&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: avoid UnsupportedOperationException&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15020775" author="jahewson" created="Sun, 22 Nov 2015 01:07:28 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15025123" author="tilman" created="Tue, 24 Nov 2015 19:08:56 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=ssteiner1&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;ssteiner1&quot;&gt;ssteiner1&lt;/a&gt; is this what you needed?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15025159" author="ssteiner1" created="Tue, 24 Nov 2015 19:28:16 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The patch in &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-3100&quot; title=&quot;Allow flexible calling of PageDrawer&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-3100&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-3100&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; has what I need, I will also wait for &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-3118&quot; title=&quot;Drop shadow missing&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-3118&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-3118&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15076644" author="jahewson" created="Sat, 2 Jan 2016 19:45:00 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The above issues are now fixed, so we&apos;re done here.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15089062" author="ssteiner1" created="Fri, 8 Jan 2016 11:02:44 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;but MaximumProfileTable and CFFCharset.getSIDForGID are not public&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15092102" author="ssteiner1" created="Mon, 11 Jan 2016 15:23:26 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I copied MaximumProfileTable to our repo so we can make use of it&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15092216" author="ssteiner1" created="Mon, 11 Jan 2016 16:24:26 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I will use reflection to call getSIDForGID&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
